  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (adversarial: COMPOUND-03)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Thirteen credibility factors assessed; assurance level declared Medium despite multiple factors with achievedLevel below requiredLevel. This package is a synthetic adversarial sample targeting COMPOUND-03: assurance-level overstatement.",
